Is this kid seriously messed-up?  Absolutely.  Is he a major asshole?  Yup.  Would I ever want to be his friend?  Not this decade, anyway.  Has he really fessed-up to everything?  I doubt it.  Is he blaming the game rather than himself?  On some levels, yes.<br>
