<br>
The kid is a dick, and if he was on the 12-step program he'd be on maybe step 1.5 but give him at least a little encouragement folks.  The alternative is to just give up and assume he'll be an antisocial asshole for life and either shot him or lock him in a room at societies expense and throw away the key.  Just think about it a bit.<br>
<br>
Val<br>
